This is a caretaker clone of biblatex 1.7 until the status of the author of biblatex is clear.
It has patches to enable certain biber-only features on top of 1.7. The documentation has also
been updated, numbers in parentheses are the section numbers of the relevant documentation section.

* Allows citekey aliases (2.2.3)
* Added an option to only sort using initials in biber (3.1.2.3)
* Added macros to allow biber's sourcemap feature to be defined per-document (4.5.1)
* The format of alphanumeric labels is now customisable (4.5.2)
